{{Top}}
A '''salvage droid''' was a type of [[droid]] that was designed for salvaging parts. The [[P-100 Salvage Droid]] was a [[repulsorlift]] model of salvage droid that was used to retrieve parts from crashed [[podracer]]s.<ref name="CL">[[Star Wars: Complete Locations (2016)|''Star Wars: Complete Locations'']]</ref>

